 und/oder Weiterbildung und an alle weiteren Interessierten, die erfolgreiche Beziehungen zu anderen Menschen aufbauen und pflegen möchten.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aCommunication in management. 0aLeadership. 4aPersonalauswahl. 4aPersonalführung. 4aPersonalwirtschaft. 4aPsychologie. 4aUnternehmensführung. 7aBUSINESS & ECONOMICS / Management.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Business and Economics 2000 - 2014z9783110635737oZDB-23-GBE08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Complete Package 2014z9783110369526oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Economics, Business 2014z9783110369649oZDB-23-DBV0 cEPUBz97831103978640 cprintz978348676377540uhttps://doi.org/10.1524/978311037519040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110375190423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110375190/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LAEC  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DBVb2014  aZDB-23-DGGb2014  aZDB-23-GBEc2000d2014